                  Without fire button pressed

                            Jump
                            
                            /|\
  Turn and Punch        /\   ^   /\    High Punch
                          \  |  /
                           \ | /
                            \|/
     Move Back <-------------0-------------> Move Forward
                            /|\
                           / | \
                          /  |  \
                         /   |   \
   Forward Somersault  \/   \|/   \/  Kneel and Punch
                          
                           Duck

