	           With fire button pressed

                        Flying Kick
                        
                            /|\
    Roundhouse Kick     /\   |   /\    High Kick
                          \  |  /
                           \ | /
                            \|/
     Back Kick <-------------0------------->  Forward Kick
                            /|\
                           / | \
                          /  |  \
                         /   |   \
 Backwards Somersault  \/   \|/   \/  Low Kick
                          
                           Sweep

